<h1 class="wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-gray-400-color has-text-color has-link-color has-grey-dark-color has-heading-hero-font-size" style="font-style:normal;font-weight:400">How to Apostille a<br><em><em><em><mark style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)" class="has-inline-color has-primary-light-color">Canadian Document</mark></em></em></em></h1>
<!-- /wp:heading --></header>
<!-- /wp:group -->

<!-- wp:paragraph {"fontSize":"medium"} -->
